<h4 id="methodology">Methodology</h4>
<p>Among the following method, OOP is most successful and famous.</p>
<ol>
  <li>Modular or Procedural Programming
    <ul>
      <li>this is in contrast with monolithic programming which means write all code in
one function.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Object Oriented Programming</li>
  <li>AOP: Aspect Oriented Programming</li>
  <li>Structured Programming</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="principles-of-object-orientation">Principles of object-orientation</h4>
<p>Just as the other industry, we want to find a way to make software, just like
making a car.</p>
<ol>
  <li>abstraction</li>
  <li>Encapsulation: Data hiding</li>
  <li>Inheritance</li>
  <li>Polymorphism</li>
</ol>

